<h2>ðŸ“· Simple Barcode Scanner</h2>

<div id="reader"></div>

<h3>Scanned Barcodes</h3>
<table id="dataTable">
  <tr>
    <th>#</th>
    <th>Barcode</th>
    <th>Timestamp</th>
  </tr>
